g-havoc-in-california-new-research-suggests-someone-deliberately-introduced-them-180988554/</guid></item><item><title>20 世纪 90 年代，一只狗教孩子们了解莎士比亚和荷马。一部新纪录片讲述“叉骨”的故事——从他的后空翻到他的历史帽子</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/in-the-1990s-a-dog-taught-kids-about-shakespeare-and-homer-a-new-documentary-tells-the-tale-of-wishbone-from-his-backflips-to-his-historical-hats-180988552/</link><description>这部电影让演员和工作人员重聚，他们看到了杰克罗素梗犬在 PBS 上将经典文学带入生活的潜力</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 15:31:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/in-the-1990s-a-dog-taught-kids-about-shakespeare-and-homer-a-new-documentary-tells-the-tale-of-wishbone-from-his-backflips-to-his-historical-hats-180988552/</guid></item><item><title>中世纪的文字和树木年轮帮助研究人员追踪 800 年前的太阳风暴并重建过去的太阳周期</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/medieval-writings-and-tree-rings-helped-researchers-track-a-solar-storm-from-800-years-ago-and-reconstruct-past-solar-cycles-180988546/</link><description>日本诗人藤原帝家的日记以及来自亚洲和欧洲的其他历史资料在一项新研究中发挥了关键作用</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/medieval-writings-and-tree-rings-helped-researchers-track-a-solar-storm-from-800-years-ago-and-reconstruct-past-solar-cycles-180988546/</guid></item><item><title>伊利湖的这艘运石船遭遇突如其来的暴风雨。 150 多年后，潜水员刚刚发现沉船</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/a-sudden-squall-doomed-this-stone-hauling-vessel-in-lake-erie-divers-just-found-the-shipwreck-more-than-150-years-later-180988557/</link><description>1868 年 9 月，一艘 125 英尺长的小船“Clough”在克利夫兰附近沉没，只有一名船员幸存并解释了发生的事情</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 13:35:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/a-sudden-squall-doomed-this-stone-hauling-vessel-in-lake-erie-divers-just-found-the-shipwreck-more-than-150-years-later-180988557/</guid></item><item><title>犹他州上空高耸的发光球体发出了紧急的艺术信息：大盐湖正在干涸</title><link>https://www.smith