f-the-american-wests-most-iconic-birds-is-attempting-to-mate-near-a-dangerous-airport-could-robo-birds-help-save-them-180988542/</guid></item><item><title>从闪闪发光的头饰到柔和的帽子，新白金汉宫展览庆祝伊丽莎白二世的时尚</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/from-sparkling-tiaras-pastel-hats-new-buckingham-palace-exhibition-celebrates-fashion-elizabeth-ii-180988526/</link><description>英国女王不仅是世界领袖，还是时尚偶像。伊丽莎白故居举办的一场新秀突出了一些最令人难忘的造型及其背后的历史</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 15:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/from-sparkling-tiaras-pastel-hats-new-buckingham-palace-exhibition-celebrates-fashion-elizabeth-ii-180988526/</guid></item><item><title>国家美术馆为美国 250 岁生日举起一面艺术镜子</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/the-national-gallery-of-art-holds-an-artistic-mirror-up-to-the-united-states-for-its-big-250th-birthday-180988538/</link><description>为了庆祝今年的五十周年纪念，“亲爱的美国”通过可追溯至 18 世纪末的艺术品来审视这个国家的土地、社区和革命历史</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/the-national-gallery-of-art-holds-an-artistic-mirror-up-to-the-united-states-for-its-big-250th-birthday-180988538/</guid></item><item><title>在主要音乐发布日，开车时要格外警惕。当顶级艺术家推出新专辑时，车祸死亡人数似乎激增</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/on-major-music-release-days-stay-extra-vigilant-while-driving-car-crash-deaths-seem-to-spike-when-top-artists-drop-new-albums-180988541/</link><description>一项新研究发现大专辑发行天数与交通死亡人数之间存在相关性。虽然研究无法证明新音乐导致了事故，但这项研究暗示了驾驶时的主要干扰因素</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 14:37:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/on-major-music-release-days-stay-extra-vigilant-while-driving-car-crash-deaths-seem-to-spike-when-top-artists-drop-new-albums-180988541/</guid></item></channel></rss>